---
title: Thyme & Caramelised Onion-Glazed Pork with Cheesy Fries & Apple Salad
description: Ain’t life a lot like good food? It’s always a balance between the sweet and the savoury. We’ve walked the tightrope
with this delicate blend of succulent pork with caramelised onion and thyme, cheesy fries and a crunchy apple salad.
Take a bite into this slice of life!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
